Package org.hkijena.acaq5.api.events

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlgorithmGraphChangedEvent
    Event is triggered when algorithm graph is changed
    AlgorithmGraphConnectedEvent
    Generated when a connection was made in ACAQAlgorithmGraph
    AlgorithmGraphDisconnectedEvent
    Generated when slots are disconnected
    AlgorithmRegisteredEvent
    Triggered when an algorithm is registered
    AlgorithmSlotsChangedEvent
    Triggered when an algorithm's slots change
    CompartmentAddedEvent
    Triggered when a sample is added to an ACAQProject
    CompartmentRemovedEvent
    Triggered when a sample is removed from an ACAQProject
    CompartmentRenamedEvent
    Triggered when a sample in an ACAQProject is renamed
    DatatypeRegisteredEvent
    Triggered when a new data type is registered
    ExtensionContentAddedEvent
    Generated when content is added to an ACAQJsonExtension
    ExtensionContentRemovedEvent
    Generated when content is removed from an ACAQJsonExtension
    ExtensionRegisteredEvent
    Triggered by ACAQRegistry when an extension is registered
    ParameterChangedEvent
    Triggered when a parameter holder's parameters are changed
    ParameterStructureChangedEvent
    Triggered by an ACAQParameterCollection if the list of available parameters is changed
    SlotAddedEvent
    Triggered after an ACAQMutableSlotConfiguration added a slot
    SlotAnnotationsChanged
    Generated when a slot's annotations are changed
    SlotOrderChangedEvent
    Triggered after an ACAQSlotConfiguration changed its slot order
    SlotRemovedEvent
    Triggered after an ACAQMutableSlotConfiguration removed a slot
    SlotRenamedEvent
    Triggered after an ACAQMutableSlotConfiguration renamed a slot
    TraitConfigurationChangedEvent
    Triggered after an ACAQTraitConfiguration was changed
    TraitRegisteredEvent
    Triggered when a trait is registered
    WorkDirectoryChangedEvent
    Triggered when the work directory of a project or algorithm was changed
